_sText: Transit - Combat/Skill ====================== This map is based off of my old "aim_transit" for Counter-Strike 1.6 (link provided below). Transit - Combat/Skill by Adam Sinclair Counter-Terrorists have cornered the T's in an underground transit system facility, near the Black Mesa complex. The T's have no choice, but to retaliate. Now it's up to each team's wits and skill to eliminate the other. Recommended 5 players / team. I'll probably be updating this if anyone has complaints. This will be my "learner" map for CSS :) Credits ======= - **Adam Sinclair:** Map layout and design - **Valve:** Textures, models, engine
